{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"996f786d73","title":"毛泽东对吴法宪检讨信的几条批注","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d8e48bb7fa","index":0,"year":1970,"month":10,"day":14,"articleId":"996f786d73"}],"tags":[{"id":"42ac79d048","name":"反潮流","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0c19d3e696","type":"title","text":"对吴宪法检讨信的几条批注","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"996f786d73"},{"id":"db10b1a01f","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"996f786d73"},{"id":"2f8b85bfb8","type":"paragraph","text":"作为一个共产党人，为什么这样缺乏正大光明的气概。由几个人发难，企图欺骗200多个中央委员，有党以来，没有见过。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"996f786d73"},{"id":"68ad07e2f0","type":"paragraph","text":"办事组各同志（除个别同志如李德生外）忘记了九大通过的党章、林彪同志的报告，又找什么天才问题，不过是一个借口。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"996f786d73"},{"id":"b86cd454cb","type":"paragraph","text":"什么伟大谦虚，在原则性问题上，从来没有客气过。要敢于反潮流。反潮流是马列主义的一个原则。在庐山，我的态度就是一次反潮流。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"996f786d73"},{"id":"e37eb2273e","type":"paragraph","text":"这句话并没有错，中央委员会有严重的斗争。有斗争是正常生活。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"996f786d73"}],"page":{"id":"bafdf33b59","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"996f786d73","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}